         * Use a factory that does not automatically resolve DTDs.
         * Otherwise, the XMLInputFactory will attempt to load DTDs
         * and external entities from the network.

         * will be removed when the deprecated methods are removed.
         */
        xmlIn = new WstxInputFactory();
